uation of their amplitude. This means\nthat such waves can still propagate from the footpoints of loop, and result in\nheating in the corona.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Jan 2023 19:51:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 13:12:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
