uisition time.\n  Conclusion: Removing inter-slab and intra-slab phase interferences enables\nSMSlab dMRI with blipped-CAIPI in a 4D k-space framework. The proposed\nblipped-SMSlab dMRI is demonstrated to be more SNR-efficient than 2D dMRI and\nthus capable of high-quality, high-resolution fiber orientation detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2023 02:49:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-10"}
